# Prompt: Recreate Adidas 3D Landing Page Preview

Recreate this above-the-fold UI at 1280px width.

## Layout & Background
- Full-viewport height, pure black background (#0a0a0a or #000)
- Content is perfectly centered both horizontally and vertically
- No header, no nav, no footer — just a single centered block

