- Use system monospace for code blocks (`-apple-system`, `Menlo`, `Consolas`, monospace)
- Body text uses system sans-serif stack

## Hero Section (centered)
1. **Main heading**: "Adidas 3D 落地页" — white (#fff), bold, large (~32-36px), centered
2. **Subheading line 1**: "该项目需要构建后才能预览。在本地执行：" — light gray (#999 or #aaa), ~16px, centered, margin-top ~16px
