4. **Subheading line 2**: "源码已原样保存在 source/2025-adidas/, 可逐文件查看/复制。" — dimmer gray (#666 or #777), ~14px, centered, margin-top ~16px

## Vibe
- Minimalist developer preview page
- Dark mode, terminal-like aesthetic
- Clean, lots of empty space around center block

