  - Rounded capsule shape (pill)
  - Border: thin light purple/white-ish outline
  - Inside text: star icon + "AWARD" in small caps
  - Color: light lavender text on transparent/dark bg
  - Font size: ~13px

## Main Content Area (centered vertically and horizontally)
Left-aligned content block positioned roughly at center-left of viewport:

