   - Font: System sans-serif (SF Pro / -apple-system), bold/heavy weight
   - Size: ~42-48px
   - Color: White (`#ffffff`)
   - Letter-spacing slightly tight

3. **Subtitle**: "Verve · 2023"
   - Font: system sans-serif, regular weight
   - Size: ~18px
   - Color: Light gray/lavender (`#b0a0c0` or similar muted purple-gray)
