   - Background: Medium purple (`#7b5cd0` or similar)
   - Text: White, ~14-15px, medium weight
   - Border-radius: Full pill (~20-24px)
   - Padding horizontal ~20px, vertical ~8px
   - Positioned below subtitle with gap ~16px

5. **Description text**: "音乐"
   - Font: system sans-serif, regular
   - Size: ~14-15px
   - Color: Muted light gray/purple (`#9999aa`)
   - Below the Awwwards pill, gap ~12px

6. **Tag/Badge (bottom-left area)**: "WebGL"
   - Small rounded rectangle tag
   - Background: Darker purple/blackish (`#251540` or similar)
   - Border: subtle thin border
   - Text: White/light gray, ~12-13px
   - Padding: ~6px 14px
   - Border-radius: ~6-8px
   - Positioned lower on the page, below description

## Typography
- System font stack: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif`
- Clean, modern, minimal aesthetic

## Colors Summary
- Page BG: `#1a1035` (deep purple-black)
- Title: `#ffffff`
- Subtitle: `#b0a0c0`
- Awwwards pill BG: `#7b5cd0`, text: `#ffffff`
- Description: `#9999aa`
- Award badge border/text: `#9080b0`
- Tag BG: `#251540`, text: `#ccc0dd`

## Spacing & Vibe
- Generous whitespace around content
- Content vertically centered, left-aligned within center zone
- Premium awards-showcase feel — minimal, elegant, dark-mode aesthetic

